<div id="myModal" class="modal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title">Rules</h5>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                <div class="container-fluid">
                    <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">Main</div>
                        <ol class="list-group">
                            <li class="list-group-item">No swearing</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">Minimum donates per week : 200</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">Participate in the clan wars: 5 in a row missed</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">Losses in clan wars: 4 in a row</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">Promotions</div>
                        <ol class="list-group">
                            <li class="list-group-item">There is one Leader - the clan founder: DjiDjiBiDji</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">There is one Co-Leader - media supporter - Kiki</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">Promotions will be given every end of the week. You can see people promotions in clan statistics page. It depends on 3 main factors: Donates, 60% Wins per Clan Wars, Trophies. Decrease also.</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">Elder can be everyone who has high trophy, actively played in clan wars and is more then a month in the clan</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">Co-leader can be everyone who has enought wins in the clan wars and is on the top 5 in the clan rank</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">Decreases</div>
                        <ol class="list-group">
                            <li class="list-group-item">You can find them in the clan statistic page. If you are marked in red you will be demoted or kicked.</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">When you are inactive or you don't follow the rules you will be decreased.</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">When you don't have minimum required donates.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                    <div class="panel panel-default">
                        <div class="panel-heading">Kick outs</div>
                        <ol class="list-group">
                            <li class="list-group-item">If you don't have minimum required donates per week.</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">If you don't play more then 4 clan wars in a row.</li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">If you don't follow the rules.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="modal-footer">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
        </div>
    </div>
